Steps to Reproduce:

1. Open the markdown preview
2. Zoom in or out

**Bug**
The preview page is reloaded.

The cause is this line in `htmlPreviewPart`:

```
	    this._modelChangeSubscription = this.model.onDidChangeContent(() => {
					if (this.model) {
						this.webview.contents = this.model.getLinesContent();
					}
				});
```


I don't know why `onDidChangeContent` is fired while zooming. We may be able to workaround the issue but it does seem odd that `onDidChangeContent` is being fired here
